        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Ἄξιον ἥγησα<supplied reason="lost">ί με</supplied> <lb n="3"/>τὸν ὠκύμορον, π<supplied reason="lost">αρο</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>δεῖτα, καὶ γνώσῃ τὰ τ<supplied reason="lost">ύχης ὡς</supplied> <lb n="5"/>ἀβέβαια πέλει· πο<supplied reason="lost">λ</supplied>λὰ γὰρ ἐν μ<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ύθοισι</supplied> <lb n="6"/>καὶ ἐν γυμνάσμασιν ὀφθεὶς ἔ<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">μπειρος</supplied>, <lb n="7"/>τύμβος καὶ κόνις ἐμβλέπ<supplied reason="lost">ομαι</supplied>· <supplied reason="lost">Ὦ </supplied> <lb n="8"/>τριτόμωμε <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Von den Z. 8-15 sind bloß einige Buchstaben noch erkannbar.</p>
            </div>
